AvlBiMap
public interface IBiMap<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue extends java.lang.Comparable<TValue>>
extends ReifiedMap<TKey,TValue>

A type-aware bi-directional AVL-tree-backed map. BiMaps require that keys and values are unique and can be accessed by key or by value.
